{"type":"message","id":"93eb44ab","parentId":"cb382a45","timestamp":"2026-02-28T05:03:21.499Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"从权限列表可以看出，当前应用主要拥有以下相关权限：\n- `docx:document` - 文档API权限\n- `docs:document.content:read` - 文档内容读取\n- `drive:drive.search:readonly` - 云盘搜索\n- `space:document:move` - 文档移动\n\n但没有看到明显的电子表格或\"sheet\"相关的权限。让我搜索一下飞书官方文档。\n\n## 第二步：搜索飞书电子表格API官方文档"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_CaNyZNduty9qKrLr46lO7xDC","name":"web_search","arguments":{"query":"飞书 电子表格 API 开放平台 文档","count":10}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-chat","usage":{"input":2050,"output":171,"cacheRead":10368,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":12589,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772254993685}}
